     <h3>Control at your fingertips</h3> 
     <p>The TVinteract app solves the problem of getting social media selected and formatted for air. TVinteract gives anchors, reporters and on-air talent the control and confidence they need, while giving producers and graphics personnel the peace of mind that the show quality will be at its best.</p> 
     <p>TVinteract technology delivers broadcast-ready and formatted tweets in real-time for network and cable stations, news broadcasts, late-night chat shows, and more.</p> 
